name: DOCS_RCVD_BIN_OBJ_COMPLD
description: This table contains the most recently received metadata for a specific binary object we could retrieve.

columns.name: DOCUMENT_ID
columns.description: This item stores the Received Document record ID.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: OBJ_LNK_RESULT_IDENT_COMPILED
columns.description: The result identifiers of the object that this object is associated with.
